summary: Adds a field. That you can plant.
descriptionHtml:
Adds a plantable field to Heljarchen Manner.
The field is attached to the garden. So you will
need to build the garden to get the field.

[b][b][b][b][b][u][size=5]Compatibility[/size]
[/u][/b][/b][/b][/b][/b][size=2]Compatible [/size]with Heljarchen REFORM.

[u][size=6][b]Requirements[/b][/size][/u]
Requires the latest version of Skyrim as well as the Hearthfire DLC.

[u][size=5]My other mods:
[/size][/u][img]http://static-3.nexusmods.com/15/mods/110/images/thumbnails/60307-1-1417066261.jpg[/img]        [img]http://static-2.nexusmods.com/15/mods/110/images/thumbnails/60309-4-1418437076.jpg[/img]
[size=2]  [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/60307/]Windstad Garden Extended[/url]                   [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/60309/]Lakeview Garden Extended[/url][/size]
